---
import Container from "@/components/Container.astro";
import SectionTitle from "@/components/SectionTitle.astro";
import FaqItem from "@/components/FaqItem.astro";
---

<Container id="faq" class="max-w-3xl">
  <SectionTitle class="mb-6">FAQ</SectionTitle>

  <div>
    <FaqItem question="Do I need improv or flirting experience?">
      None at all. Flirt Improv is built for total beginners and seasoned flirts
      alike. All you need is a willingness to play, laugh, and be a little
      silly.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="Is this a dating event?">
      No. It's a creative workshop for practicing flirtation, not a place to
      find dates. If a spark happens, we handle introductions privately after
      the event through our feedback form.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="How much does it cost?">
      Usually a small fee to cover the space and materials. Exact pricing goes
      out with each event announcement.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="How long does it run, and what happens?">
      About two hours, with time to mingle before and after. It's a no-audience,
      full-participation session of warm-up games, flirting scenarios, cheesy
      pick-up lines, and storytelling.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="Who tends to come?">
      Adults 18+ of every experience level and relationship type. We aim for a
      rough male/female balance to keep the flirting dynamics natural, but
      everyone is genuinely welcome.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="What should I bring or wear?">
      Casual, comfortable clothes, like a fun night out with friends. Bring your
      best (or worst) pick-up lines, an open mind, and a sense of humor.
    </FaqItem>
  </div>
</Container>
